{"type":null,"faqId":26082,"title":"如何群发短信？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.009722223in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.6736112in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.1.1\"></a><span>在主屏幕界面，点击“信息 &gt; </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.1.1.1.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.1.1.1.2.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90989\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.17986111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.2.1\"></a><span>在收件人输入框中添加多个收件人：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">−  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>点击收件人输入框可输入多个收信人号码。每输入一个号码后点击“；”以隔开各联系人。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">−  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.2.2.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.2.2.2.1\"></a><span>点击收件人输入框右边的 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.2.2.2.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.2.2.2.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90990\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.17986111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>” 可添加多个收信人。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e790\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90991\" style=\"width:2.6930556in;height:3.9402778in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.3.1\"></a><span>点击“键入信息”输入短信内容。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.4.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.4.1\"></a><span>点击“</span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.4.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.1.4.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90992\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.17916666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>” 群发短信。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.3.2.2\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90993\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":168,"faqType":"信息与电子邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"402","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Messaging-Emailing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1432262699000,"seriesProductName":"T1-A21w","visitedTimes":21,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage"